Scene

HandTool: 
Panel of 5 icons (on top left in Unity)
- Move: click and drag
- Orbit: alt + click and drag
- Zoom: alt + righ click and drag
(ctrl + click)
- Hold shift quickly zoom (Does not work with scroll wheel)


FlyThrough Mode:

perspective: view is first person shooter

Isometric: No perspective. Everything looks the same size

Orthographic: Looking down 1 plane (no camera orbiting) 

Scene View Gizmo can be clicked to change from iso to perspective
Align Camera buttons XYZ

2D vs 3D button

Wireframe, Shaded also very important scene views

light button toggle

audio button toggle

skybox, fog, flares and animated materials toggle

search form

